Package: lines
Title: Nice and Easy Terminal Input
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Salvatore Sanfilippo, Pieter Noordhuis, Yuji Hirose, Gabor Csardi
Maintainer: Gabor Csardi <csardi.gabor@gmail.com>
Description: Read a line or a paragraph from the terminal.
    It supports ANSI colors and UniCode characters. It also supports
    input history and TAB completion. It is based on the 'linenoise'
    library by Salvatore Sanfilippo.
License: BSD_2_clause + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/gaborcsardi/lines
BugReports: https://github.com/gaborcsardi/lines/issues
Suggests:
    testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
SystemRequirements: C++11
